  body
    .mobile-warning
      h2 Hey! It looks like you're using a mobile phone, which is awesome.
      h2 But we spent a lot of time making this application look juuuust right for desktop, and it'll probably be a little squishy on your phone.
      h2 (But it should still work!)
      h2 If that's OK with you,&nbsp;
        a(href='#', do='close-warning') tap here
        | .
      h2 Otherwise, come back on your computer later, ok? ;)
    iframe(name='dupe-frame')
    .formula
      .header
      .next-btn
        .inner-btn
          span Submit!
      form
        .primary-window.page.current
          .forcefield
            .input-group
              input#name(type="text", name='entry.2104495372', required)
              label Name (First and Last)
              .glance
            .input-group
              input#email(type="email", name='entry.1061169608', required)
              label School Email
              .glance
              .pill-right
                span .edu
            .input-group
              input#hearsay(type="text", name='entry.1597876375', required)
              label How did you hear about our application?
              .glance
          .thanks
            h3 Thanks! We'll let you know as soon as the app is ready  :D
            img(src="./images/fyeah.png")

